    0.5%, 1.2%, 3.5%.
6. ["Results of a "GWAS Plus:" General Cognitive Ability Is Substantially Heritable and Massively Polygenic"](http://journals.plos.org/plosone/article?id=10.1371/journal.pone.0112390), Kirkpatrick et al 2014:

