3. ["Common genetic variants associated with cognitive performance identified using the proxy-phenotype method"](http://www.pnas.org/content/early/2014/09/05/1404623111.full.pdf), Rietveld et al 2014 ([supplementary](http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC4183313/bin/pnas.1404623111.sapp.pdf))

